This picture of the Prince Brand and Princess Astrid is available in Falador, bought from Sir Renitee for 1,000 coins. Completion of Throne of Miscellania is necessary to purchase this portrait. It may be framed in one's player-owned house with 55 Construction, two mahogany planks and hung in the Quest Hall. The result of doing so is the Miscellanians portrait.
